achment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Morrissey和Sparks乐队成员Ron和Russel Mael" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025_morrissey_sparks_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025_morrissey_sparks_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025_morrissey_sparks_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025_morrissey_sparks_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025_morrissey_sparks_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025_morrissey_sparks_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Morrissey">莫里西（Morrissey）</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sparks">Sparks</a>上打了出来，称他们为“无头的帕利萨德斯（Palisades）野蛮人，他们将老朋友扔进了热熔融熔岩进行性感踢脚”。</p><p>这位前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-Smiths">史密斯（Smiths）的</a>主持人在Instagram帖子中的二人组进行了挖掘，其中包含90年代的一系列照片。</p><p>其中一张图片的特点是Sparks的笔记，谈论当时正在研究的一堆演示。</p><p>莫里西（Morrissey）在帖子旁边的标题中写道：“罗恩（Ron）和罗素·梅尔（Russell Mael）的不错的音符 - 在他们变成了无头的帕利萨德（Palisades）野蛮人之前，他们把老朋友扔进了热熔融熔岩中，以获得性感的踢脚。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DHoMLX0Ices/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; m