/03/ljg-album@2000x2000-1068x1063.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3849103" class="wp-caption-text">劳拉·简·格雷斯（Laura Jane Grace）在创伤的“冒险俱乐部”艺术品中。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><p>在其他劳拉·简·格雷斯（Laura Jane Grace）新闻中，去年，这位歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/laura-jane-grace-interview-hole-in-my-head-against-me-reunion-3584582">与<em>NME</em>谈到了她的专辑“ Hole in My Heard”</a> ，并回顾了开创性朋克专辑“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-against-me-15027-316392">Transpergender densphoria Blues</a> ”的10周年。</p><p>她谈到后者时说：“这很疯狂，以为已经整整十年了。” “这一切都像昨天一样直接感到直接。我非常感谢那张唱片周围发生的一切，我为那张唱片感到自豪。”</p><p> “我看着那时的地方，我想，&#39;那是我吗？&#39;就像，“那是现实吗？” “我过着那个生活，因为它与此没有什么不同吗？”她补充说。</p><p> “当我写唱片时，我什至没有出来。我什至还没有出来。甚至在出来后一年之内发生的变化数量是如此他妈的令人难以置信的思维和巨大。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/laura-jane-grace-in-the-trauma-tropes-announce-new-album-adventure-club-with-capitalism-bashing-single-mine-me-mine-3849094">劳拉·简·格雷斯（Laura Jane Grace）在创伤性的劳拉（Laura Jane）格雷斯（Tropes）宣布新专辑“冒险俱乐部”，资本主义击打单曲“ Mine Me Mine”</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
幽灵的托比亚斯（Tobias）伪造了一个转变为电影的转变：“我开始认识到我可能有一个地方的地方” https://www.nme.com/news/music/ghost-tobias-forge-forge-forge-forge-hints-aift-aift-shift-into-film-industry-3849074?utm_source = rs = rss间Damian JonesTue, 25 Mar 2025 15:52:09 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetalRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3849074 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025_ghost_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="鬼魂" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025_ghost_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025_ghost_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025_ghost_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025_ghost_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025_ghost_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025_ghost_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>乐队备受期待的第六张录音室专辑“Skeletá”下个月发行</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ghost-tobias-forge-hints-at-a-shift-into-film-industry-3849074">《幽灵邮报》的托比亚斯（Tobias）伪造暗示了一部电影的转变：“我开始认识到我可能在哪里有一个地方”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025_ghost_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="鬼魂" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025_ghost_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025_ghost_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025_ghost_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025_ghost_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025_ghost_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025_ghost_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ghost">Ghost</a>的Tobias Forge暗示他可能会更多地参与电影制作。</p><ul><li><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/tobias-forge-interview-new-material-future-of-ghost-black-sabbath-metal-scene-3847292"><b>托比亚斯（Tobias）锻造新材料和幽灵的未来：“如果粉丝需要传说喜欢乐队，那么该元素将很快结束”</b></a></li></ul><p>在乐队备受期待的第六张录音室专辑“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ghost-announce-new-album-skeleta-share-new-anthemic-lead-single-satanized-3843730">Skeletá</a> ”之前，这位金属主持人<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/tobias-forge-interview-new-material-future-of-ghost-black-sabbath-metal-scene-3847292">在新的采访中与<em>NME</em>进行了交谈</a>，该专辑定于4月25日发行。</p><p>福格（Forge）在瑞典神秘乐队（Swedish Gacult Band）的时期居住了一系列不同的角色，多年来，乐队的图像受到了电影的影响。</p><p>当被问及他是否考虑过更多地参与电影界时，福格说：“绝对。我一直对电影的感兴趣，就像我从事音乐一样感兴趣。但是，由于我不是一个非常学的人，所以很快就在学校里[我觉得我]就可以发展到天花板上的范围。</p><p> “如今，您可以过上成功的生活而没有受过深厚的教育，但是当时，我觉得有一定程度的学术主义需要进行电影。</p><p>他继续说道：“在我的生活中，我看到了一条企业，因为这条路线将从我的音乐中消失，并且需要我开始学习的东西。但是，现在，我已经倾向于电影世界，我开始认识到我可能有一个地方的地方。我相信我可以有价值的地方。我相信我可以走那条路线。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Ghost的Tobias Forge在新专辑“Skeletá”上，克服了早期挣扎并从传说中继续前进" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZbWuqhWpo_o?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在同一次采访中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ghosts-tobias-forge-on-the-misconception-that-rock-is-dead-we-are-living-proof-that-its-not-true-3848331">福格说鬼魂是“生命证明”，即“岩石死了”的概念不是真的</a>。他说：“我并不是说您可以成为新的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ac-dc">AC/DC</a> ，但我们可以证明您仍然可以做到这一点。” “最近有更多的乐队，例如<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sleep-token">Sleep Token</a> ，他们都在成功，因此很明显，您可以成为一个更大的乐队。”</p><p>该乐队即将发行的专辑最近以其动画主角“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ghost-announce-new-album-skeleta-share-new-anthemic-lead-single-satanized-3843730">撒旦化</a>”而预览，这是Forge新的Persona <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ghost-tease-new-frontman-papa-v-perpetua-with-las-vegas-billboard-v-is-coming-3842804">Papa Perpetua的</a>首位。</p><p> Ghost也是在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-sabbath-final-show-birmingham-july-2025-metalla-slayer-pantera-line-up-tickets-3835042">Black Sabbath即将在伯明翰的Villa Park举行的决赛</a>的众多乐队之一。福格说：“<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-sabbath">黑安息日</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ozzy-osbourne">奥兹·奥斯本</a>对我有很大的影响。” “我作为主持人和奥兹（Ozzy）作为独奏艺术家是我之间的分歧，因为我在80年代长大，他比黑安息日更像是摇滚明星。</p><p> “I gravitated towards that, but I also grew up listening to the old Black Sabbath records. Nowadays, I love most Black Sabbath releases. Even the &#39;80s and &#39;90s albums, I love them for what they are, and the <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ronnie-james-dio">Dio</a> era also has a very special place in my heart, too.”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tobias-forge-on-ghosts-phone-free-rule-for-2025-world-tour-its-so-hard-to-get-people-to-engage-3844635">Ghost are heading on their own tour around the UK, Europe and the US next month</a> , starting in Manchester&#39;s AO Arena on April 15. Find the full list of dates <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ghost-announce-2025-world-tour-with-shows-in-the-uk-europe-us-and-north-america-buy-tickets-3807064">here</a> and any remaining tickets in the UK <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fghost-tickets%2Fartist%2F1878819" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a> and US <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.com/ghost-tickets/artist/1878819?irgwc=1&amp;clickid=Rqx2TC0vSxycWqXz1YU1iXMmUks3rDWyx2Cb2s0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;impradid=2862475&amp;REFERRAL_ID=tmfeedbuyat2862475&amp;wt.mc_id=aff_BUYAT_286